        "body": "<p>So, I found what I was looking for built into netty, I've been using it for a few days now and haven't posted back.<\/p>\n\n<p>Inside of netty there is a <code>ChannelBufferInputStream<\/code> and a <code>ChannelBufferOutputStream<\/code> these both take in the ChannelBuffer as a parameter and allow similar functions to that of a DataStream. It has really helped me with my networking. <\/p>\n",
